text: Anastasiia Yurievna Harnyk (; born 10 September 1995) is a Ukrainian Paralympic judoka. She won a gold medal at the 2024 Summer Paralympics. == Career == Anastasiia Yurievna Harnyk was born 10 September 1995 in Kyiv, Ukraine. She is blind. On 9 August 2023, she won first place at the in Rotterdam. On 7 September 2024, she won a gold medal at the 2024 Summer Paralympics in Paris. == References == == Other websites == * Category:1995 births Category:Judoka Category:Living people Category:Paralympic gold medalists for Ukraine Category:Sportspeople from Kyiv
